  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Establishes the crime of larceny of a controlled substance making it an A-II felony to steal more than 25 dosage units of a schedule II, III, IV, or V controlled substance from a pharmacy."
    }
